#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.52"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.52:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.52:0.2"
msgid "6. Brāhmaṇavagga"
msgstr "6. Brahmins"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Dutiyadvebrāhmaṇasutta"
msgstr "52. Two Brahmins (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.156"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.52:1.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho dve brāhmaṇā jiṇṇā vuddhā mahallakā addhagatā vayoanuppattā "
"vīsavassasatikā jātiyā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te "
"brāhmaṇā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ:"
msgstr ""
"Then two old brahmins—elderly and senior, who were advanced in years and had "
"reached the final stage of life, being a hundred and twenty years old—went "
"up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to the Buddha:"

msgctxt "an3.52:1.2"
msgid ""
"“mayamassu, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā jiṇṇā vuddhā mahallakā addhagatā "
"vayoanuppattā vīsavassasatikā jātiyā;"
msgstr ""
"“We brahmins, Master Gotama, are old, elderly and senior, we’re advanced in "
"years and have reached the final stage of life; we’re a hundred and twenty "
"years old."

msgctxt "an3.52:1.3"
msgid "te camhā akatakalyāṇā akatakusalā akatabhīruttāṇā."
msgstr ""
"And we haven’t done what is good and skillful, nor have we made a shelter "
"from fear."

msgctxt "an3.52:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ovadatu no bhavaṃ gotamo, anusāsatu no bhavaṃ gotamo yaṃ amhākaṃ assa "
"dīgharattaṃ hitāya sukhāyā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Advise us, Master Gotama, instruct us! It will be for our lasting welfare "
"and happiness.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.52:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Taggha tumhe, brāhmaṇā, jiṇṇā vuddhā mahallakā addhagatā vayoanuppattā "
"vīsavassasatikā jātiyā;"
msgstr "“Indeed, brahmins, you’re old, elderly and senior."

msgctxt "an3.52:2.2"
msgid "te cattha akatakalyāṇā akatakusalā akatabhīruttāṇā."
msgstr ""
"And you haven’t done what is good and skillful, nor have you made a shelter "
"from fear."

msgctxt "an3.52:2.3"
msgid "Āditto kho ayaṃ, brāhmaṇā, loko jarāya byādhinā maraṇena."
msgstr "This world is burning with old age, sickness, and death."

msgctxt "an3.52:2.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ āditte kho, brāhmaṇā, loke jarāya byādhinā maraṇena, yo idha kāyena "
"saṃyamo vācāya saṃyamo manasā saṃyamo, taṃ tassa petassa tāṇañca leṇañca "
"dīpañca saraṇañca parāyaṇañcāti."
msgstr ""
"But restraint here by way of body, speech, and mind is the shelter, "
"protection, island, refuge, and haven for the departed.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.1"
msgid "Ādittasmiṃ agārasmiṃ,"
msgstr "“When your house is on fire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.2"
msgid "yaṃ nīharati bhājanaṃ;"
msgstr "you rescue the pot"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.3"
msgid "Taṃ tassa hoti atthāya,"
msgstr "that’s useful,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:3.4"
msgid "no ca yaṃ tattha ḍayhati."
msgstr "not the one that’s burnt."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: Evaṃ āditto kho → evaṃ ādīpito (bj, pts1) | evaṃ ādittake (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "an3.52:4.1"
msgid "Evaṃ āditto kho loko,"
msgstr "And as the world is on fire"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:4.2"
msgid "jarāya maraṇena ca;"
msgstr "with old age and death,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:4.3"
msgid "Nīharetheva dānena,"
msgstr "you should rescue by giving,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: sunīhataṃ → sunibbhataṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an3.52:4.4"
msgid "dinnaṃ hoti sunīhataṃ."
msgstr "for what’s given is rescued."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.1"
msgid "Yodha kāyena saṃyamo,"
msgstr "The restraint practiced here—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.2"
msgid "Vācāya uda cetasā;"
msgstr "of body, speech, and mind—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.3"
msgid "Taṃ tassa petassa sukhāya hoti,"
msgstr "leads the departed to happiness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "an3.52:5.4"
msgid "Yaṃ jīvamāno pakaroti puññan”ti."
msgstr "as the good deeds done while living.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.52:5.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
